* Creating a terraform workspace helps to avoid creating multiple terraform projects for differnt evironments like dev,QA,stage.

* Same project can be used in different enovironment by creating terraform workspaces

* Terraform workspaces helps to create the separte statefile for each environment.

* To create a workspace for dev environment use the below command
     terraform workspace new dev

* To create a workspace for stage environment use the below command
     terraform workspace new stage

* To create a workspace for prod environment use the below command
     terraform workspace new prod

* Terraform command to switch between the environments(switch to dev env)
      terraform workspace select dev

* Terraform command to show in which environment we are working
      terraform workspace show
      

